<br>
If it aint scary it aint fun! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :evil --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/devil.gif ALT=":evil"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Air travel has taken all the fun out of traveling abroard, dont let it take the fun out of space! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
As somebody else said eslsewhere. Spacehips need to be impressive and awesome. I know I am in a minority (of one probabally) in favoring ground launched Orions. But can you imagine *anything* more awesome than a the launch of a 400,000 ton (or more) Orion?<br>
